re has to be enough stock and you must have enough points.\\n\\nTo track an order, you just have to click on the section  \\"My Winnings\\" in the menu. "},{"question":"Do I have to pay for shipping costs ?","reponse":"No, shipping costs are free of charge."},{"question":"What is the delivery time for prizes ?","reponse":"The delivery time varies according to our suppliers. Please allow 7-14 days  for delivery. Unfortunatly, this can take up to three weeks when our suppliers\' products are out of stock. \\n\\nConcerning bank cheques and gift vouchers, these are sent once a week. "},{"question":"When is the shop restocked ?","reponse":"Concerning the VIP shop, it restocked every day.\\n\\nConcerning the Auction room, as soon as a prize is sent, it is automatically replaced."},{"question":"I live overseas, can I receive my orders ?","reponse":"We do our best to send the prizes to foreign players. If ever a shipment is not possible, we offer a refund or the possibility to exchange your prize for an equivalent one."},{"question":"Why can\'t I have access to the Shop ?","reponse":"Players who did not reach the Explorer I level have to go to the Auction Room to place an order."},{"question":"Is there a random draw ?","reponse":"There is no random draw in our shop, a gift you win is a gift you receive."},{"question":"My order has been \\"Confirmed (in progress)\\" for more than a week, why ?","reponse":"The delivery time can take up to three weeks for some of the prizes. \\n\\nIf your prize has not been sent, it might be because you did not enter your address in the space provided in \\"My personal information\\", in the section \\"My account\\". \\n\\nOur interface can only confirm your prize under this condition. .\\nMake sure that your contact details are well indicated. \\n\\nIf this is not the case, please contact our Customer Service to give us your full address, or directly fill in the space provided when clicking on \\"My personal information\\". "},{"question":"Ho