hrough your mobile operating system (iOS or Android). They use the standard SSL (Secure Socket Layer), that is to say the highest security level for secure Web applications."},{"question":"Can we see all the payments made on the application ?","reponse":"Yes, you just have to click on the section \\"My account\\" in the menu and to choose the tab \\"Payments\\" "}]},{"titre":"VIP levels and advantages","articles":[{"question":"What are VIP levels ? What are my advantages ?","reponse":"We offer a lot of advantages to our players. \\n\\nAccording to your level, Seaman, Pirate, Captain, you will benefit from many advantages.\\n\\nTo know how to access the different levels as well as the advantages offered by each of them, please click on the section  \\"VIP levels\\" in the menu.\\n\\nPlease note that only the credits obtained in the section \\"Credits\\" in the menu are taken into account and enable you to get ahead.\\n\\nOn this page, you can also know how many credits you need to reach the next level."},{"question":"How to reach a new level ?","reponse":"You just need to get game Credits from the section \\"Credits\\" in the Menu and to meet our requirements indicated in the section \\"VIP levels\\" in the Menu.\\n\\nEach time you reach a new level, you benefit from new advantages."}]},{"titre":"My account","articles":[{"question":"How do I change my email address ?","reponse":"To change your email address, click on the section \\"My account\\" in the menu, then on  \\"Email\\".\\nYou will find a specific frame to change your email address.\\n"},{"question":"How do I change my username ?","reponse":"To change your username, click on the tab \\"Username\\" in the section \\"My account\\" in the menu. Enter your new username in the space provided, then confirm your choice.\\n\\nPlease note that you can only change your username once.\\n\\nIf you cannot change your username, please contact the Customer Service who will make the necessary handlings."},{"question":"How do I change my password ?","reponse":"To change your password, click on the tab \\"Password\\" (section \\"My account\\" in the main menu), change your password and confirm. The passwords you will type must be identical, otherwise the modification will be refused. \\n\\nIf you cannot change your password, please contact our Customer Service who will make the necessary handlings."},{"question":"Where do I have to indicate my postal address ?","reponse":"To update your postal address, click on the button \\"My account\\" in the main menu, then on \\"Address\\". \\nEnter your contact details and confirm your choice.\\n\\nWe recommend players living outside France to enter their full postal address.\\n\\nWe do not oblige you to enter your telephone number but it is highly recommended in case our transporters need to contact you when delivering your prizes."},{"question":"How do I confirm my user account and/or my registration email address ?","reponse":"Your account will only be active when you click on the link sent by email following your registration.\\n\\nIf you did not receive the confirmation email, please check your spam folder. We recommend you to add us to your address book so that you can receive our emails.\\n\\nOtherwise, if you win a prize, you won\'t receive the email informing you of your prize !"},{"question":"I have received a message from the website, where can I find it ?","reponse":"To find all the answers sent by our Customer Service, you just have to click on the button \\"Help\\" in the Menu, then on the button \\"Customer Service\\". When you receive a message, an alert appears on the top of the application. "},{"question":"How to unsubscribe ?","reponse":"You want to leave us to sail off to new horizons ?\\n\\nTo unsubscribe, you just have to make a cancellation request to our \\"Customer Service\\". We would be grateful if you would explain us the reasons why you want to cancel your account and what we should improve."}]},{"titre":"Referring","articles":[{"question":"How to refer a friend ?","reponse":"To refer a friend, you just have to click on the button \\"Referring\\" in the menu then to choose to send a text message or an email. Depending on your choice, an email or a text message will be sent to your future friends and you will win 200 Points per registered friend.\\n\\nBut your friends can also name you as their referring person when registering.\\nThey just have to enter your player code in the space provided. You can find the player code in the tab \\"Personal information\\" in your account.\\n\\nIf your friend registers by himself, he/she will have to enter this code in the space  \\"Referring code (optional) \\"."},{"question":"What does \\"Confirmed\\" mean ?","reponse":"Congratulations ! Your friend has been accepted and you can benefit from all the advantages of referring a friend, that is to say:\\n\\n- Win from 200 to 400 Points for each Friend according to your VIP level\\n- Win 5% of the Points obtained by your friends on classic games according to your VIP level\\n- Win 2 Credits for each friend who reaches the Buccaneer level.\\n- Win a Gift Voucher of 25,000 Points for each friend who reached the Pirate III level.\\n- Win a Gift Voucher of 75,000 Points for each friendwho reaches the Captain level.\\n\\nYour friend has been accepted because he meets the following requirements: \\n-Registered on LudoKado with your referring code\\n- Confirmed his account by clicking in the registration email \\n- Have been confirmed by the LudoKado team (within 5-7 days from the registration date)"},{"question":"What does \\"Refused\\" mean ?","reponse":"LudoKado has no reason to refuse a friend ! Except for players who try to refer themselves (fake friends registration). It is very important to respect article 3.7 of LudoKado\'s Terms of use, it is a matter of respect towards the website and overall towards other players :\\n\\n\\" Referring new players is completely free of charge. All LudoKado\'s members can refer new players. When a new player registers thanks to another member, he becomes one of his friends. There is no limit to the number of friends for each referring person, but \\"self-referring\\"is forbidden, at risk of removal for good from LudoKado.\\"\\n\\nIn general, with a view to guarantee respect and fairness between players, the confirmation criteria for a user account is in our \\"Customer Service\\"hands."},{"question":"What does \\"Pending\\" mean ?","reponse":"When you refer a friend, it is automatically saved in the section \\"Referring\\" in the Menu, then \\"Friends\\".\\n\\nAs long as a friend is not registered, you can send him an invitation email. \\"Pending\\" means that you sent the email to this person but he/she did not registered on the website and/or that the customer service did not confirm the referring. This confirmation is done within 5-7 days following the registration day of your friend. Once it confirmed, you will receive all the advantages."},{"question":"My friend did not receive the email I sent him, why ?","reponse":"Are you sure you entered the right email address ?\\n\\nMake sure it is correct, or your friend may have received it in the spam folder. If it is the case, your friend just has to find the email and notice his messaging service that this is not a spam by entering the email address info@ludokado.com\\n\\nRemind you that your friends can name you as their referring person when registering by themselves. They just have to enter your player code in the space provided on the registration form.\\n\\nYou can find your player code in the section \\"My account\\" tab \\"Personal information\\""}]}]';
